snippet: The state fisheries commissioner announced that Maine’s lobstermen last year harvested more than 100 million pounds of lobster, the biggest catch ever.
abstract: Maine fisheries commissioner says Maine’s lobstermen harvested more than 100 million pounds of lobster in 2011, the biggest catch ever.
lead_paragraph: The state fisheries commissioner announced that Maine’s lobstermen last year harvested more than 100 million pounds of lobster, the biggest catch ever.
